Library of MTK video codec driver utility, icluding video codec specified m4u, memory allocate, 
memory map, command queue related funcitons to help decoder fullfilling it's functionality.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
libvcodec_utility contains MediaTek developed video decoder related utilites.
Without them, video playback & record functionalities will not work¡¨

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1.  libcutils.so
2.  libsched.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1.  libbwc.so
2.  libm4u.so
3.  libgralloc_extra.so
4.  ibion.so
5.  libion_mtk.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Provide utility api for SW codec and HW codec HAL to control the video codecs.
all api interface are at (device/mediatek/common/kernel-headers)

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
